I think its really funny how in an instant everything can change. We are so close to having a 3rd world war and no one knows it. We can be dead in a matter of minuets. There are nuclear weapons that can destroy us in an instant. It is quoted from alber enistein although not exact along the lines of " i do not know what weapons will be used for the 3rd world war,...but by the 4th..they will be using sticks and stones."  makes you think? it sure has hell made me think. Everything can change in an instant..no second thought just gone. I realized this walking home. How quickly my life can change by one event. For instance I could be hit by a car walking home because we have no distinct sidewalks. I could die, or be paralized or it could just be life changing. But it doesnt matter beucase everything changed. Medical bills would go through the roof and the greif that overwhealmed my family and friends would effect them. Scarry to think about... To know that in an instant in 10 seconds your life could change forever. We have so many things we take for granted and we dont even realize it. Studying the World War and the Industrial Revolution for example showed how women lived in the 19th century. Poor lives, worked for less than minimum wage and couldn't go to school and didn't get paid the same amount as a man did for the same job. And working at home..they would get paid half of what the woman was making working at the factory. Maybe someone will take a look over their life and ask themselves if they really like whats happening. Maybe yes and maybe no..I looked at my life this summer before I knew this and I changed many things. For example my need for a guy. I finished so many things this summer and im happier with the way that i am. Well just take at look at yourself and whats around you.. Do you really like it? Do you really want to live this way?

I reallly wanna WAKEBOARD. I kinda figured it out today when I was watching tv with my mom...I really want the excitement of doing flips and turns and the falls. I want it so bad!! I want to get good and to be sponsored and maybe even be signed... I want it so bad. Im willing to do anything just to be able to get good at least and be able to do flips and stuff. I'm not that good right now but I really wanna be. I've never wanted something this badly. I got all excited about it over dinner tonight.My plan was to get good, be sponsored, enter competitions, win them, be signed. Everyone who knows me knows that im not one to be all excited about sports and actually wanna do it. Basketball turned out to be a strictly fun game with friends. But Wakeboarding...I want it to be so much more. So I guess im getting lessons this winter maybe. Im willing to go out and buy a wet suit if i need it and a new board if i really have to. I want this so bad...
